    "description": "<strong>FIREFIGHT RELOADED</strong> is a brutal Half-Life 2 mod focused on massive swarms of enemies and fast-paced, movement oriented gameplay.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HALF-LIFE 2 GAMEPLAY: REDEFINED</h2>Inspired by boomer shooters, Killing Floor, Titanfall, and Half-Life 2 mods like SMOD, <strong>FIREFIGHT RELOADED</strong> focuses on fast-paced, movement oriented gameplay. Run, shoot, grapple, slide, kick, and wallrun through ever-intensifying hordes of enemies and unlock new perks, weapons and items to become stronger. The mod also includes an in-game store that allows you to purchase items with with in-game currency acquired by killing enemies and playing the mod. Analyze every kill with the bullet time slow-motion feature that can be activated at any point. Utilize precisely-placed headshots and explosives to bring upon brutal annihilation of your enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OLD AND NEW ARMAMENTS, OLD AND NEW ENEMIES</h2>Fight in various locations from the Half-Life games and rip apart old, new and familiar foes with a sandbox of old, new and familiar weapons. Weapons have been modified with new firing modes and iron sights for those wishing for a more “tacticool” experience. They can be used in conjunction with movement options for powerful and brutal kills.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZATION A-PLENTY!</h2>Don’t like how FIREFIGHT RELOADED plays? You have full control over how enemies, weapons, and game mechanics behave with an ever-growing amount of options at your disposal. Find new maps, map information files, items for the in-game shop, loadouts, skins, gamemodes, NPCs and weapons on the Steam Workshop.",
